Packages
de.frag.umlplugin This package contains classes and interfaces like providers and consumers used for dependency injection on actions.
de.frag.umlplugin.actions All base actions used in several different toolbars are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.anim This package contains classes for animating graph elements.
de.frag.umlplugin.classcloud This package contains classes that analyze dependencies between classes and compute a layout that is able to display several hundred or even several thousand classes in a single diagram.
de.frag.umlplugin.classcloud.actions All actions that are related to the class cloud diagram are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.codenavigator This package contains the classes that directly belong to one of two project components.
de.frag.umlplugin.codenavigator.actions All actions that belong to the graphical navigator are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.codenavigator.graph Classes used for creation of graphs needed for graphical navigator are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.graphio General graph I/O classes are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.guilayout Provides classes for easy creation of complex GUI designs.
de.frag.umlplugin.history Classes related to graphical navigation history are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.icons This package contains all icons used in toolbars and menu items.
de.frag.umlplugin.psi Dependencies between classes are analyzed and stored by classes in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.scopes Classes can be filtered by search scopes.
de.frag.umlplugin.settings Classes related to plugin settings are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml Provides core classes for UML diagrams.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.actions Provides actions related to UML diagrams.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.actions.edgepopupmenu Actions used in popup menu shown on right clicking UML-diagram-edges are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.actions.nodepopupmenu Actions used in popup menu shown on right clicking UML-diagram-nodes are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.actions.toolbar Actions used in toolbar shown above UML-diagrams are contained in this package.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.command Provides all classes that implement UML diagram creation steps.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.diagramio This package contains classes for storing UML-diagrams as XML-, GIF-, JPG-, PNG-, SVG- and GraphML-files.
de.frag.umlplugin.uml.graph Provides some general graph related classes.
